{"tid":598712,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"冰川拔絲黑豚肉","createTime":"2018-03-19T17:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T13:37:43.000Z","uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c9aabb553d290eb47280aefd4e68be22a7344341","tid":598712,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"收工經過深水埗諗住食個頹飯先返屋企<br />\n見到間茶記新開 核核突突<br />\n但d小菜名就好有霸氣<br />\n叫左個冰川拔絲黑豚肉<br />\n一上枱原來係咕嚕肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌左聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/015128_7ddcae44fd353e32c3a4f7414dc423f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F015128_7ddcae44fd353e32c3a4f7414dc423f5.png&h=1637ec83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街 未撚食過咁撚好食嘅咕嚕肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來同個老闆傾計<br />\n話係用蛋白漿炸，所以個皮又脆又薄<br />\n肉真係用黑豚肉，所以改個咁嘅名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老闆好靚仔"},{"pid":"ae1e10e30557178662504cdcbe9d002420f17942","tid":598712,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9aabb553d290eb47280aefd4e68be22a7344341","tid":598712,"uid":69218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"收工經過深水埗諗住食個頹飯先返屋企<br />\n見到間茶記新開 核核突突<br />\n但d小菜名就好有霸氣<br />\n叫左個冰川拔絲黑豚肉<br />\n一上枱原來係咕嚕肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌左聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/015128_7ddcae44fd353e32c3a4f7414dc423f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F015128_7ddcae44fd353e32c3a4f7414dc423f5.png&h=1637ec83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街 未撚食過咁撚好食嘅咕嚕肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來同個老